name: Deliberated mixed
description:
This is a mix of many different Models, to play around with the model merge feature of aiNodes which once again has produced a wonderfull result.

The Models in this mix and in that order are

deliberate_v11, babes_11, elldrethsLucidMix_v10, woopwoopPhoto_12, hassanblend1512And_hassanblend1512

They all got mixed at 0.5 one after the other.

There is plenty triggers which can be found in the original models. To show the mix brings together the goods of all the Models I reproduced a few of their Prompts. The results look different for sure but they stilll show the originals features.

aiNodes can be found here: https://github.com/XmYx/ainodes-pyside

Find our Discord: https://discord.gg/VRqwu89Vrw
